{
  "stem": "523.1",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- and I'd be caught because this the 14-years-old boy, what I happen to know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How many people that I don't remember were caught?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because everybody knew that what's happening when we are going out of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was a question of survival.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "No matter what, you will die.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this was the life in-- in-- in Bershad.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, there is all over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I'm talking just Bershad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It's one place that I have been.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Transnistria-- it was 300,000 people died in Transnistria.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They thing is that why is nobody know about Transnistria?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because it was never on the map.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was just a piece of land, Ukraine, and they gave it a name, that never existed.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after the Russian came in 1944, it ceased to exist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's why when people ask me, Freda, where have you been during the war, and I say Transnistria, they ask me trans-what, or trans-where?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I never heard about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This is very painful when you know that over 300,000 Jews, Romanian people, Jewish from Ukraine, died in this piece of land.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And nobody knew and heard about it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is very painful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "An author wrote a book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was called-- about Transnistria.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was called",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that's exactly what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because all of Transnistria is like a big cemetery with mass graves-- no stone, no sign, no-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody didn't know what happens, where it happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this is because when the Russian eventually liberated us, we all became Soviet citizen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There's no mentioning nowhere that those Jewish survivor Romanian Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But for the Romanian, we were the Communist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "For the Russians, we were who knows what-- never mentioned that we are Jewish survivors.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's what happened.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This is Bershad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "TIll-- This is the place where I was.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
